# Paths semgrep must skip. Providing this file REPLACES semgrep's built-in
# default ignore list. That default silently ignores "tests/", which hid all
# non-ASCII in our test files (semgrep flagged 32 files where grep found 47).
# We deliberately DO NOT ignore tests/ here so the no-non-ascii rule sees them.
venv/
.git/
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
*.egg-info/
postgres-17/
postgres-data/
*.duckdb
*.db
*.log
